long_desc: Discover this secret beauty weapon straight from the Amazonian jungle. The Rahua by Amazon Beauty 100-percent organic hair care products contain the pure and powerful Rahua nut, an ancient hair care remedy of the indigenous Quechua Indians, who also harvest the ingredients for this amazing line. The finishing treatment prevents hair from splitting during styling, blowdrying, hot ironing and combing. Silicone-free, it provides a glossy, weightless finish with rich, organic ingredients. The finishing treatment contains rahua oil, which leaves hair smooth, shiny and frizz-free; ungurahua oil keeps hair firmly rooted; rich bran wax seals moisture; green tea leaf extract minimizes UV damage and raspberry leaf extract rich infuses hair with antioxidants. The elixir rebuilds and repairs damaged hair, through a highly concentrated and highly potent formula. It contains rahua nut oil, which rebuilds the most damaged stresses and ungurahua oil with rejuvenating omega-9 to strengthen the hair follicle.
